Blockers
- Finish/test MetaData merging and filtering
- Add missing tests
- Update README

Nice-to-have
- Re-enable proguard on .jar
- Add strict mode checks to tests


Build/test/release instructions
-------------------------------

Run tests on device or emulator

    gradle :connectedCheck

Build a new jar/aar files:

    gradle :build

Build and release a new version to maven central:

    gradle :uploadArchives

Build and install the example app:

    gradle example:installDebug
